WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Re_fle_chi' is a Workbench game that is played on an 8 by 8
spaces game board that is divided in 4 'quadrants' of 4 by 4
spaces. The idea is to move diagonal bars so they form a
kaleidoscopic pattern in all 4 quadrants. If this sounds easy,
the game is all but simple: Every time you click on a diagonal
bar from one quadrant, one bar from each of the 3 other quadrants
will also move.

  ...And do not think that by changing a bar that has been changed
in another quadrant, that it will change the same "corresponding"
bars that have previously been changed... That other bar may
change other bars in the other quadrants, which add some more
confusion to an already confused situation!

  However, to help you a little bit; when you click and re-click
on the same bar it will always change the same bars in the other
quadrants...

  Can you complete the game in the least amount of moves possible?

  Have fun!

